modName: Norse Themed Tattoo Pack for RaceMenu
summary: Adds a number of Norse themed overlays to RaceMenu
descriptionHtml:
Includes 18 unique overlays with variations of some for a total of 30 overlays.

[b]Compatibility:[/b]
All overlays were designed to be used for UNP bodies and should be compatible with all UNP body types including SevenBase which were used in the screenshots.

[b]Tools Used:[/b]
[url=http://www.gimp.org]GIMP[/url]
[url=http://code.google.com/p/gimp-dds]GIMP DDS Plugin[/url]

[b]Required Files:[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu by expired6978[/url]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org]SKSE[/url]
